Cardiometabolic risk in childhood cancer survivors.

Luongo C(1), Randazzo E(2), Iughetti L(3), DI Iorgi N(4), Loche S(5), Maghnie 
M(4), Valerio G(6), Delvecchio M(7).

Author information:
(1)Department of Woman, Child, General and Specialized Surgery, Luigi Vanvitelli 
University of Campania, Naples, Italy.
(2)Unit of Pediatric Endocrinology and Diabetes, Department of Clinical and 
Experimental Medicine, University of Pisa, Pisa, Italy.
(3)Unit of Pediatrics, Department of Medical and Surgical Sciences for Mothers, 
Children and Adults, University of Modena and Reggio Emilia, Modena, Italy.
(4)Department of Pediatrics, IRCCS Istituto Giannina Gaslini, Genoa, Italy.
(5)Unit of Pediatric Endocrinology, Ospedale Pediatrico Microcitemico &quot;A. 
Cao, &quot; Cagliari, Italy.
(6)Department of Movement Sciences and Wellbeing, University of Naples 
