Proximal iliac limb extension and embolization: a new technique of complete 
endovascular management of an unfavorably sited type III endoleak.

Bellam Premnath KP(1), Parkinson TJ(1), Pancione L(1), Salih AT(1).

Author information:
(1)Barking Havering and Redbridge University Hospitals NHS Trust, Queen's 
